    <item>
      <title>丰业银行表示，加拿大央行的措施表明其比市场想象的更为鹰派</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/bank-of-canada-measures-suggest-it-s-not-ready-to-ease-scotiabank-s-derek-holt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新斯科舍银行经济学家德里克·霍尔特表示，加拿大央行决定恢复多年来未使用的现金管理工具，这表明政策制定者不想很快开始放松货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/bank-of-canada-measures-suggest-it-s-not-ready-to-ease-scotiabank-s-derek-holt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:59:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球 ESG 债券销售在有史以来最繁忙的 1 月份达到 1500 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/global-esg-bond-sales-reach-150-billion-in-busiest-january-ever</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可持续债券销售经历了有记录以来最繁忙的一月份，因为较低的借贷成本引发了交易热潮，而债务的顶级承销商则增加了销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/global-esg-bond-sales-reach-150-billion-in-busiest-january-ever</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:50:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>广告低迷期间 Snap 裁员约 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/snap-reduces-workforce-by-about-10-amid-ad-slump-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Snap 在全球范围内裁员约 10%。 Snap 在一份文件中表示，此次裁员是为了“让我们的业务处于最佳位置，以执行我们的最高优先事项”。西蒙·福克斯曼报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/snap-reduces-workforce-by-about-10-amid-ad-slump-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:45:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>林德纳表示，德国经济增长乏力使国家变得更加贫穷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/lindner-says-germany-s-lack-of-growth-is-making-country-poorer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳表示，由于未能实现经济增长，德国变得越来越贫穷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/lindner-says-germany-s-lack-of-growth-is-making-country-poorer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:28:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡特彼勒的能源和运输销售推动盈利增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/caterpillar-tops-estimates-on-energy-and-transportation-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的重型机械制造商之一卡特彼勒公司(Caterpillar Inc.)在报告其能源和运输业务第四季度销售额增加后，消除了对全球经济放缓的担忧，这帮助其公布的利润超出了分析师的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/caterpillar-tops-estimates-on-energy-and-transportation-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 11:33:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
